description: If the U.S. figure skater wants gold in his first Olympics, his quads will be crucial.
title: The Quad Jump Is Changing Figure Skating. Nathan Chen Is Leading the Way.
title_page: The Quad Jump Is Changing Figure Skating. Nathan Chen Is Leading the Way. - The New York Times
maintext:
Yes, you heard that right. Chen’s practically keeping track of his points during his entire routine. Attempt a jump in the second half of a program? An extra 10 percent.
It doesn’t hurt that he just got a perfect score on his math SATs.
